OPENING EXERCISES

President Chad Diviney called the meeting to order at 6:31 p.m. All present were asked to
Stand and pledge allegiance to the American Flag.

REORGANIZATION OF THE BOARD

Nominations were received for Temporary President. Mr. Robert Seprish nominated Mr. Donald
Yontosh as Temporary President. Mrs. Christina Brown seconded the motion, and it was carried by a
vote of 9-0-0.

Method of nomination was determined for Board President and Vice President. Mr. Jeremiah Dobo
motion to nominate Board President and Vice-President from the floor. Mr. Melvin Smeal seconded the
motion and it carried with a vote of 9-0-0.

Nominations were received for Board President. Mr. Donald Yontosh nominated Mr. Chad Diviney for
Board President.

Mrs. Christina Brown motioned to close nominations, and it was seconded by Mr. Robert Seprish. The
motion carried with a vote of 9-0-0.

Mr. Norman Parks motioned to elect Mr. Chad Diviney as Board President. Mrs. Christina Brown
seconded the motion, and it was carried with a vote of 9-0-0.

Nominations were received for Board Vice-President. Mr. Chad Diviney nominated Mrs. Christina Brown
for Board Vice-President.

Mr. Norman Parks motioned to close nominations, and this was seconded by Ms. Jessica Maines. The
motion carried with a vote of 9-0-0,

Mr. Jeremiah motioned to elect Mrs. Christina Brown as Board Vice-President. Mr. James Emigh
seconded the motion, and it was carried with a vote of 9-0-0.

Mr. Chad Diviney took over the meeting as Board President.

