carried by a vote of 9-0-0.

D. Consiglio Mr. Donald Yontosh, in the form of a motion, recommended to appoint David Consiglio

Solicitor as Solicitor to the District for the 2023 year. Mr. Melvin Smeal seconded the motion,
and it was carried with a vote of 9-0-0. Mr. Consiglio offered his thanks to the Board
and he also expressed his appreciation for Mrs. Dutrow’s service. He looks forward to
continuing with the District.

ADJOURNMENT

Mr. Don Yontosh, in the form of a motion, recommended to adjourn the meeting 6:48 p.m. Mrs.
Christina Brown seconded the motion and it carried with a vote of 9-0-0.

The Board then moved to the regular voting session.
